POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123ghghghgh7+{}",
  "userName": "Test User",
  "userShortName": "TU",
  "code": "12345"
}

### Login:
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123ghghghgh7+{}"
}

### Verify user:
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/verify
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..zE6rEd4yXk08utqXTCbeHl25ZNoW65O7TFC6_ArGnzg

### Logout user:
